   "text": "BEAT 10 \u00b7 total views + the age hook\nSEE: About panel, marker on the views row\nVOICE: \"Over 40 million total views.\" \u2014 and if\nthe channel is under ~9 months old: \"Keep in\nmind, they started posting only 5 months ago\"\n+ a wow-line; under 18 months: said plainly;\nolder: age never mentioned",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "center",
   "verticalAlign": "middle",
   "containerId": "aCBs8q1Afksmplr9",
   "originalText": "BEAT 10 \u00b7 total views + the age hook\nSEE: About panel, marker on the views row\nVOICE: \"Over 40 million total views.\" \u2014 and if\nthe channel is under ~9 months old: \"Keep in\nmind, they started posting only 5 months ago\"\n+ a wow-line; under 18 months: said plainly;\nolder: age never mentioned",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
