   "text": "BEATS 12-18 \u00b7 the money math\nSEE: a run of white cards + one shrug icon \u2014\nthe math plays out card by card, ending in a\ngiant green dollar figure with a \"ding\"\nVOICE: \"Even if we assume just a 3 dollar RPM\u2026\nthat's roughly\u2026 36 THOUSAND DOLLARS\u2026\nfrom ads.\" (a \"mostly US viewers\" line is added\nsometimes, only when the RPM is high)",
