   "text": "Then the recording is sliced per beat at word\nboundaries \u2014 pauses land naturally \u2014 and text\ncards pop their words at the exact spoken moment.\nSlightly sped up to match the genre's pace (~167\nwords per minute).",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "center",
   "verticalAlign": "middle",
   "containerId": "e9hAetagAhmxtwjd",
